space complexity: O(N*M) where N is the number of words and M is the average length
energy implications: LOW
explanation: Uses a nested-dictionary trie structure; each node is a dict keyed by character. '#' marks word ends. All operations traverse the trie once, giving optimal time complexity and minimal memory overhead.

